text: The 2009 NCAA Division I Men's Swimming and Diving Championships were contested in March 2009 at the Student Recreation Center Natatorium at Texas A&M; University in College Station, Texas at the 86th annual NCAA-sanctioned swim meet to determine the team and individual national champions of Division I men's collegiate swimming and diving in the United States. ==Team standings== *Note: Top 10 only *(H) = Hosts *(DC) = Defending champions *Full results {| class="wikitable sortable" style="text-align:center" |- !Rank !!
